  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375\u00040F (190\u00040C).",
    "In a large skillet, brown the rest-meat over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the unsalted butter and let it melt, then sprinkle the all-purpose flour over the rest-meat and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Gradually stir in the mirin-hon and bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce heat to low and simmer for 5 minutes.",
    "In a separate pan, saut\u00055 the large onion until translucent, then set aside.",
    "Combine the cooked onion with the rest-meat mixture, chopped fresh dill, and white pepper."
